summary: SummaryGet instant volume for your lashes! L'Oréal Paris Voluminous Lash Paradise Volume Mascara gives your lashes instant breathtaking volume and length. The formula is infused with a luscious blend of flower oils - lashes feel conditioned and supple to the touch.
details: DetailsBenefitsThe Lash Paradise Mascara Formula Is- clump-resistant, smudge-resistant, longwearing and suitable for sensitive eyesFormula is infused with flower oils and lashes feel conditioned and supple to the touchEasy To Use- The ultra-soft wavy brush catches every eye lash for dense, fuller-looking voluminous lashesFeaturesGet volume and length in an instant - Give your lashes instant breathtaking volume and length for up to 24 hour with Lash Paradise MascaraSmooth glide formula provides silky volume in one coatSoft wavy bristle brush holds maximum formula for a dramatic volumizing charge200+ bristles catch every lash for a full fringe effectItem 2510037How To UsePlace brush at base of lashes and gently sweep to the tip. Repeat as desired, Gentle and easy to remove with soap and water.To safeguard L'Oreal purity, reserve this product for your personal use. Treat the applicator with the hygienic care you give your eyes. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle. Do not dilute mascara with water, saliva, or any other substance. Cap tightly after use. If change in odor or appearance occurs, discontinue use. Do not use this or any other eye cosmetic if your eye is injured, irritated or infected. Consult a physician promptly.IngredientsBlackest Black: Aqua/Water/Eau, Paraffin, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, Copernicia Cerifera Cera/Carnauba Wax/Cire De Carnauba, Ethylene/Acrylic Acid Copolymer, Styrene/Acrylates/Ammonium Methacrylate Copolymer, Cera Alba/Beeswax/Cire Dabeille, Synthetic Beeswax, Bis-Diglyceryl Polyacyladipate-2, Polybutene, Cetyl Alcohol, Steareth-20, Glyceryl Dibehenate, Steareth-2, Phenoxyethanol, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Acacia Senegal Gum, Tribehenin, Caprylyl Glycol, Glyceryl Behenate, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Hydrogenated Jojoba Oil, Hydrogenated Palm Oil, Disodium EDTA, Butylene Glycol, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Silica, Tetrasodium EDTA, Potassium Sorbate, BHT. May Contain: CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499/Iron Oxides, CI 77007/Ultramarines.

reviews.headline: Mascara
reviews.comments: To much mascara on the brush!

reviews.headline: Great for whimpy menopause lashes
reviews.comments: I've tried so many different mascaras, some really expensive, and this one is terrific and well priced. My lashes have shortened and thinned with age and this is the only one that makes my lashes full, long and pretty again. I use the black/brown. I teach outside in the heat and it even holds up to sweat.

reviews.headline: I would not buy this product
reviews.comments: Not for thin lashes. Not for sensitive eyes

reviews.headline: Lashes,Lashes!
reviews.comments: This mascara works wonders!(The amount of compliments I've got wearing this is crazy)It's become a staple in my makeup routine. It lasts against school air, and makes my lashes look like falsies. the brush I slightly on the larger side so you have to be carful with application. As someone who likes a more dramatic lash look, you can overapply this product. Other than that if you focus with application you can get amazing results!

reviews.headline: Amazing lashes
reviews.comments: This mascara makes my lashes look so much longer it is a key stable in my makeup routine everyday!

reviews.headline: I would buy this again.
reviews.comments: Great coverage

reviews.headline: Great Mascarra
reviews.comments: I have used Paradise for many years and would not change to anything else.  It never clumps, runs, or fades.  I usually use two coats and it always looks natural and never looks like "spider" lashes.  The brush is great and it does give alot of volume as advertised.  Very good product and highly recommend.  No need for falsies if you use this mascara.

reviews.headline: My new go to!
reviews.comments: Add volumes and length with no clumps

reviews.headline: Not the same
reviews.comments: i find this product has changed a lot. It's dry and overly sticky almost like your at the end of the tube and seems like it last a lot less. I'll be looking for another brand.

reviews.headline: Better than too faced!
reviews.comments: So my favorite mascara for a few years was the Too Faced better than sex mascara, BUT I gated how the Too Faced would flake off through the day!! I saw that this mascara's packaging and everything looked almost identicle to the Too Faced and decided to try. Its now been my favorite for the last 4 years!! It works just like to Too Faced and is a great dupe and it DOES NOT flake onto the face!! Its easy to apply, not clumpy & its more cost effective. Highly recommend to anyone that likes the Too Faced, or someone looking for a great mascara!

reviews.headline: Its pretty good
reviews.comments: It does not hold a curl well, and eaily gets clumpy, but it also makes my lashes look great. Overall it's pretty good but there probably better options out there.

reviews.headline: It flakes off.
reviews.comments: I was surprised that this mascara flakes off. Disappointing.

reviews.headline: worth the try
reviews.comments: Thought I would give this a try since the price was great, rating was pretty good and the online appearance of the product seemed to be something I would like. Tired of paying big $ for a mascara that is just so so. Have been using this for a couple of weeks now and like the look. Not as stark as black and the brush doesn't give you a clumpy look.

reviews.headline: 0 out of 10
reviews.comments: This mascara is horrible and got SO clumpy after just a couple uses.

reviews.headline: Hard to find not black mascara
reviews.comments: I am pleased to find mascara that is not black. Even black brown is too harsh

reviews.headline: L'Oreal voluminous lash paradise volume mascara
reviews.comments: I love this mascara, as it really fills in my lashes.  I like the price that it is affordable.  I like your sales also.

reviews.headline: My favorite mascara
reviews.comments: Love this stuff!!! Makes lashes voluminous and long. Keeps a curl all day. Feels like a prestige mascara at a drugstore price. Only con is that it dries out quicker than other mascaras…but I don't mind having to restock more often because the price is better than other brands.

reviews.headline: This thing sucks
reviews.comments: Its hard to take off. When i switched to this mascara my lashes look stubby and clumpy. Dries out really fast and basically no product. Get something else.

reviews.headline: I will continue to buy this product
reviews.comments: This product is everything it says and then some.  Voluminous Lash Paradise Mascara is voluminous. Provides so much volume it's almost like having false eyelashes!

reviews.headline: No
reviews.comments: Nice they have a black/brown color. It's drying and clumpy and irritating to my eyes. Yuck.

faceoff_positive.comments: This is the mascara of my dreams. I use to use the better than sex mascara but it irritated my eyes, flaked, was hard to remove, and was $24! I've been on the hunt for a mascara that could replace that one and after almost two years, and dozens of failed mascaras I have found it. this one is the best mascara I have ever used. Yeah, I said it. It lengthens, separates, adds volume, doesn't clump, and holds the curl of my natural lashes! The pictures i'm posting are literally ONE COAT! One! I'm in lash paradise! :D
faceoff_positive.headline: YES!

faceoff_negative.comments: I usually buy Voluminous but it's been transferring under my eyes (even with waterproof) so I decided to try this. The result on my lashes were OUTSTANDING! I get so many compliments. And ZERO mascara under my eyes with non waterproof. I bought black waterproof and 2 tubes of black non waterproof. Why so many? I'll tell you. This mascara has a shelf life like I've NEVER seen before. Maybe a month and a half OR LESS  then it's totally dried up! Had I not gone online and read reviews, I may have kept thinking it was somehow me?! I love this mascara but cannot waste anymore money on new product drying up so PLEASE FIX THE DRY OUT PROBLEM. So disappointed.
faceoff_negative.headline: Great for full long Lashes; BAD shelf life!
